description: Here at Mainland, we believe that good things take time. This is why Mainland's tasty cheddar is aged up to 12 months for a sharp flavour. For a convenient and delicious lunch on the go, we've paired Mainland's aged cheddar with wheat crackers and tangy balsamic beetroot relish.
